## Definition of Done

- Completed KanbanZone cards move to **"Ready to Release to the World"** (Expedite), **"Final Review"** (normal development), or **"Reflection / Learning"** (business) — never directly to "DONE". A staging environment review step is required before cards are considered done.
- The `## Verified` section in commit messages serves as a required sign-off on how each change was validated.

## Discrepancy Rule

If any discrepancy exists between a repo's CLAUDE.md and AGENTS.md, it must be flagged immediately and the user asked for repair instructions.

